OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely dry
OL,6,Fthroughout Monday evening with late
OL,7,Fsunny spells. A band of showers
OL,8,Fspreads eastwards overnight, turning
OL,9,Flocally heavy around dawn. A rather
OL,10,Fcool night for June, especially under
OL,11,Fany prolonged clear spells.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FA day of sunshine and
OL,14,Fblustery showers, with the showers
OL,15,Fpossibly turning heavy in places. An
OL,16,Fisolated chance of thunder in the
OL,17,Fnorth. Temperatures a little below
OL,18,Faverage.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
